The gallery macro should accept a boolean param for pagination - plus how many pics to show per page. We have a page with 400 pics on it using the macro and if we could limit a page to just say 25 pics and then navigate using pagination that would reduce the server load significantly. The issue is when we send out a notice to our staff saying new pics are posted, then everyone comes and looks - we need pagination.

